; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 1125-1127
; Tests auto-xact cost derivation when the auto-generated amount is
; negative and has ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT (from @@ syntax).
; The (-amount) expression produces a negative kWh amount with @@ cost
; annotation, triggering the in_place_negate() of the derived cost.

= Expenses:Energy
    Assets:Refund    (-amount)
    Liabilities:Tax  (amount)

2024/03/01 Electric Bill
    Expenses:Energy       100 kWh @@ 72 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test reg --generated
24-Mar-01 Electric Bill         Expenses:Energy             100 kWh      100 kWh
                                Assets:Checking              EUR-72       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
                                Assets:Refund              -100 kWh       EUR-72
                                Liabilities:Tax             100 kWh       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
end test
